import {Component, Injectable} from '@angular/core'; import {Router} from "@angular/router"; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) @Injectable({providedIn: 'root'}) export class AppComponent { constructor(private router: Router){ } public registerHere(pageName: string): void{ const button = document.createElement('button'); button.type = 'button'; button.style.display = 'none'; button.setAttribute('data-toggle', 'modal'); this.router.navigate([`${pageName}`]); } }
